namespace pdg { /**

\class Point
\brief point for 2D coordinate system

Point provides support for dealing with points as x, y floating point values
in 2 dimensional space. The PDG coordinate space starts with the top left corner of the drawing port at 
Point(0,0) and the bottom left corner at Point( width, height );

